<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="blanket-n">blanket <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'blæŋkɪt/    美 /'blæŋkɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>毯子；毛毯；毛毯似的东西：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I took a thick blanket and wrapped it around her.
我拿了一条厚毯子裹在她身上。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a blanket of snow / fog
厚厚的一层雪/雾</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="a-wet-blanket">a wet blanket</h3>
<p>1.<strong>扫兴的人；泼冷水的人</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>It’s cold today. Please put another <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (毯子) on the bed.  （2008 陕西）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. blanket  </p></div>